article_text:
Investigators are searching for the person responsible for a bank robbery Saturday just before 11 in the morning.

Pima County Sheriff's deputies say the robber struck at a Chase bank near Oracle and Rudasill.

No one was hurt. The robber got away with an undisclosed amount of cash.
